  • Classes in com.poesys.db.dao.query used by com.poesys.db.dao 
    Class and Description
    IKeyListQuerySql
    An interface that defines the set of operations required by an IQueryListWithKeyList object to build and parameterize a SQL SELECT statement for a set of data transfer objects (DTOs) specified by a list of key values associated with the SQL statement through an IN clause.
    IKeyQuerySql
    An interface that defines the set of operations required by an IQueryByKey object to build and parameterize a SQL SELECT statement for an IDto.
    IParameterizedQuerySql
    An interface that defines the set of operations required by an IQueryListWithParameters object to build and parameterize a SQL SELECT statement for a set of data transfer objects (DTOs) specified by a set of parameters defined in a second DTO
    IQueryByKey
    An interface for Command-pattern data access objects (DAOs) that query by a key within a data transfer object (DTO)
    IQueryList
    An interface for a Command class that queries a list of data transfer objects (DTOs)

    An interface for a Command class that queries a list of data transfer objects (DTOs).

    An interface that defines the set of operations required by an IQueryList object to build a SQL SELECT statement for a set of data transfer objects (DTOs)

    An interface for a Command class that queries a list of data transfer objects (DTOs).

    QueryByKey
    An implementation of the IQueryByKey interface that implements the basic elements of a query by primary key.

    An implementation of the IQueryList interface that queries a list of data transfer objects (DTOs) based on a SQL statement with no parameters.
    QueryListWithKeyList
    An implementation of the IQueryList interface that queries a list of data transfer objects (DTOs) based on a parameterized SQL statement and a list of keys.
    QueryListWithParameters
    An implementation of the IQueryListWithParameters interface that queries a list of data transfer objects (DTOs) based on a parameterized SQL statement.
